{"tid":2170960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度逮捕中共間諜 控其行賄百名藏僧介入達賴轉世","createTime":"2020-08-23T15:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T18:42:29.000Z","uid":370345,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d557e0d7932cb7d50c88199c4bdb0121888c8e72","tid":2170960,"uid":370345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>印度逮捕中共間諜 控其行賄百名藏僧介入達賴轉世</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一名自稱羅桑（Luo Sang）、化名為查理．彭（Charlie Peng）的中國男子於8月11日在印度新德里被捕，印度當局認為，他涉嫌洗錢以及從事一個秘密行動，為的是行賄西藏僧侶，以便介入達賴喇嘛轉世靈童的遴選過程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cnnnews18/status/1296796613277396995?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnnnews18%2Fstatus%2F1296796613277396995%3Fs%3D21&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=14e6a938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcnnnews18%2Fstatus%2F1296796613277396995%3Fs%3D21&h=e1fc1ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cnnnews18/status/1296796613277396995?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n印度政府消息人士向News18透露，查理．彭過去2年來，可能行賄了大約100名喇嘛，以便能爭取他們支持中共政府心儀的靈童候選人繼承達賴喇嘛。據悉查理彭都是用現金行賄，也會用電匯。<br />\n<br />\n調查期間，印度當局訊問了卡納塔克邦（Karnataka）與北方邦（Uttar Pradesh）兩個寺廟里的僧侶。<br />\n<br />\n印度當局本月初展開查稅行動時逮捕了查理．彭，並對他提出告訴，罪名包括洗錢以及行賄僧侶，據悉行賄金額在2,700-4,000美元之間（約台幣8.2萬-12.4萬），借此收買僧侶取得有關西藏精神領袖達賴喇嘛的情資，並「滲透」進他的核心圈。"},{"pid":"a34fd1c3bd84d83d029005157fac1e514588d096","tid":2170960,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44238c8863d593d2bd7f62ab14c18feeb6a8f056","tid":2170960,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bc139a53c95ae74495ce29e4776bfc193ecabf","tid":2170960,"uid":362827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"等睇割蓆，準備同班阿叉係花廳大戰三百回合喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f6d99fa0c21ea24a97ea31d4ce8e8f6729be08","tid":2170960,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d5941e2e0d8149970bdb5750ab5f06d270a28a","tid":2170960,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:39:37.000Z","msg":"印度搶晒疆<br />\n抵你做下個世界工廠"},{"pid":"52024e01f0f8c3c0519e5dc45f82468613faa59e","tid":2170960,"uid":100772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"而家個班宗教領袖好明顯奶哂共 唔知收左幾多"}]}